---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: "Frequently asked questions"
description: "Practical VoiceTel FAQ covering accounts, pricing, voice, messaging, hosted PBX, emergency service, compatibility, and support."
---

<p class="eyebrow">Help</p>
<h1>Answers for buyers, developers, and telecom operators.</h1>
<p class="lede">The FAQ answers operational questions directly and routes readers to pricing, docs, or support when a detail depends on account configuration.</p>
<p class="hero-actions">
	<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup/">Sign Up</a>
	<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/docs/">Read docs</a>
</p>

<div class="faq-search">
	<label class="visually-hidden" for="faq-search-input">Search the FAQ</label>
	<input type="search" id="faq-search-input" data-faq-search placeholder="Search the FAQ — try 'KYC', '10DLC', 'CNAM'…" autocomplete="off">
	<p class="faq-search__status" data-faq-status aria-live="polite"></p>
</div>

<div class="faq-layout">
	<nav class="faq-nav" aria-label="FAQ categories">
		<p class="faq-nav__heading">Categories</p>
		<ul>
			{%- for cat in faqs.categories %}
			<li><a href="#{{ cat.id }}" data-faq-nav>{{ cat.label }}</a></li>
			{%- endfor %}
		</ul>
	</nav>

	<div class="faq-content">
		{%- for cat in faqs.categories %}
		<section id="{{ cat.id }}" class="section-block faq-block">
			<h2>{{ cat.label }}</h2>
			{%- for item in cat.items %}
			{%- set qid = "q-" ~ (item.q | slugify) %}
			<details class="faq-item" id="{{ qid }}">
				<summary>
					<span class="faq-item__question">{{ item.q }}</span>
					<a class="faq-item__anchor" href="#{{ qid }}" aria-label="Permalink to this question">#</a>
				</summary>
				<div class="faq-item__answer">{{ item.a | safe }}</div>
			</details>
			{%- endfor %}
		</section>
		{%- endfor %}

		<p class="faq-empty" data-faq-empty hidden>No questions match that search. <a href="/contact/">Ask support directly</a> or <button type="button" data-faq-clear class="faq-empty__clear">clear the search</button>.</p>
	</div>
</div>

<aside class="cta-block" aria-labelledby="faq-cta-heading">
	<h2 id="faq-cta-heading">Question not answered here?</h2>
	<p>The FAQ covers the questions buyers ask most often. Specific deployment, compliance, or integration questions are usually fastest answered by spinning up an account and talking to engineering inside the portal.</p>
	<p class="hero-actions">
		<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup/">Try for Free</a>
		<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/docs/">Browse docs</a>
	</p>
</aside>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
	"@context": "https://schema.org",
	"@type": "FAQPage",
	"mainEntity": [
		{%- for item in faqs.flat %}
		{
			"@type": "Question",
			"name": {{ item.q | dump | safe }},
			"acceptedAnswer": {
				"@type": "Answer",
				"text": {{ (item.plain or item.a) | dump | safe }}
			}
		}{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
		{%- endfor %}
	]
}
</script>
